# text = The new comer understood, and began in a low tone to give a very terrified account, to which the king listened calmly, while Guillaume Rym called Coppenole’s attention to the face and dress of the new arrival, to his furred cowl, (_caputia fourrata_), his short cape, (_epitogia curta_), his robe of black velvet, which bespoke a president of the court of accounts.
